target: What day and time would you like to travel?
context: <user>  I sure hope so. I'd like to find a place to stay, with four stars, in the north. <system>  I have about 8 options for you. They are all guesthouses. Do you have a preferred price range? <user>  Price is not of any concern, just so it has a 4 star rating. <system>  What dates would you like to stay? <user>  Oh, I think I forgot to mention that it needs to be a 4 star guesthouse. I want to book Saturday for 7 people 2 nights. <system>  All the 8 hotels are 4 star hotels. I recommend the Avalon or the Archway House. Should I book one of those for you and your party? <user>  Yes, please book a reservation. <system>  I have successfully booked you for avalon. Reference number is RI8WLX7E . Do you need anything else?<user>  Thank you! I also need info on trains that are leaving Cambridge. <system>  Sure, where are you headed?<user>  kings lynn is my destination <system>
